name: White Flag (for the Oceans) II
description: Video & Audio from an 8 hour durational Performance Art piece by Artist & Environmental Activist Carmen Danae Azor @carmendanae. The digital artwork is about raising a white flag for the Oceans and all the species we've already lost to extinction due to anthropogenic causes. 100% of the sale & royalties will go towards Ocean Conservation & Climate Action projects in the Dominican Republic where the performance took place. Video Duration: 60seconds, Dimensions: 3824 × 2160  #WorldArtDay2021
